Attributions
------------------------------------------------------------------------

BLE HID keyboard implementation patterns (BluetoothHidDevice registration,
Boot Keyboard HID report descriptor, SDP settings) were informed by Google's
WearMouse project, also licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0:

    WearMouse
    Copyright 2018 Google LLC
    https://github.com/google/wearmouse

The USB HID Boot Keyboard report descriptor follows the USB HID 1.11
specification (Appendix E.6), a public standard.

This project does not bundle WearMouse source code; the BLE HID layer
(BleHidManager, HidReportDescriptor) is an independent implementation.
